data.description: Experience the epitome of comfort and convenience in this stunning 3 bedroom, two bathroom ranch-style home nestled in the heart of Stockbridge. Spacious open floor layout, this residence offers an ideal setting for first time buyers seeking tranquility without sacrificing accesiblity.      With its close proximity to shopping centers, restaurants and major expressways, convenience is at your fingertips.  Whether you are unwinding in the cozy living spaces or entertaining guests in the backyard,  this home is sure to impress with this blend of style and functionality.  Discover your dream home in Stockbridge!      Owner-occupied.  Home is NOT vacant.
